开放给其他厂商使用。预计近年内高端旗舰影像手机将仍以 1 英寸 CMOS 为主。 IT 之家附 MX989 参数信息如下： CMOS 实际尺寸为 1.02 英寸，5000 万像素，采用了 4:3 的比例，而不是常规的 3:2 比例。 IMX989 采用了先进的制程，拥有更快的读出速度、兼顾进光量和分辨率的 Quad-Bayer 色彩阵列，以及让每个子像素都拥有对焦能力的 Octa-PD 相位检测对焦系统。这款 CMOS 支持像素融合，融合像素面积可达到了 3.2µm，更适合暗光拍摄。消息称有手机厂商定制 M43 画幅主摄，比 1 英寸 IMX989 更大"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-abab24de4d0341d205bb715a4d56addb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599017727"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I97Ks+bm4wqoDEAMaCDk1Mzk1NzExILbfzaIGMAE4SUAkcgk1OTkwMTc3Mjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1683439781.2170284", "card_id": "Q_594599262", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 85}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "下班后能用来运动的时间不多，想获得最佳健体效果，是短时间快跑合适，还是长时间慢跑更好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-32a005a59b5095f7f44670610410e85a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/594599262"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I97Ks+bm4wqoDEAMaCDk0NDE0NDI1IOP9yqEGMAg4sgJAJXIJNTk0NTk5MjYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1683439781.2176151", "card_id": "Q_599316533", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 107}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "未来数字人民币将为居民消费、存款理财等带来哪些变化？还可能出现哪些新的应用场景？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d61497085af41d09f54becfe2cbcceed_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": 